item.title: CVE-2019-10744|2024-08-04T22:32:01.271Z -- snyk -- lodash
item.description: Versions of lodash lower than 4.17.12 are vulnerable to Prototype Pollution. The function defaultsDeep could be tricked into adding or modifying properties of Object.prototype using a constructor payload.
